; Regression test for issue #1607: Make timeclock transactions balanced (BZ#535)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1607
;
; Timeclock transactions (i/o entries) should create balanced double-entry
; postings. Currently they create only a single posting with no offset,
; resulting in a non-zero balance total. A balanced transaction would require
; a second posting (e.g., to Equity:Time or similar) so that the journal
; balances to zero.

i 2013/03/28 10:00:00 Projects:Consulting
o 2013/03/28 14:00:00

; Current (broken) behavior: only one posting exists, balance is non-zero
test bal
               4.00h  Projects:Consulting
end test
